code: @Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj != null && obj.getClass() == BroadcastVariableKey.class) {         BroadcastVariableKey other = (BroadcastVariableKey) obj.         return this.superstep == other.superstep && this.name.equals(other.name) && this.vertexId.equals(other.vertexId).     } else {         return false.     } }
